Package pl.polsl.matrixcalculatorweb.model

Class MatrixTableModel<T extends Number>

java.lang.Object
javax.swing.table.AbstractTableModel
pl.polsl.matrixcalculatorweb.model.MatrixTableModel<T>
Type Parameters:
T - generic type which represents the type of matrix's elements extending Number class
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, TableModel
public class MatrixTableModel<T extends Number> extends AbstractTableModel
A class in the 'model' package. The class represents a model of table containing matrix's data passed by user. The class extends AbstractTableModel class.
